{"id": "1492001442725105707", "channel_id": "1492001442725105707", "type": 0, "author_id": "437363640849399818", "author_name": "far0w1", "author_bot": false, "content": "As a slay the spire player the dtide is really the least roguelite mode there is, which is fine for an end game mode but not when there are upgrade and gear mode behind it. Fine if I have to play the mode at least allow us to auto farm it, so I can get the materials for account progression and play the mode I like for example the new train mode.\n\nI actually don’t like either the dive or the dtide especially when there is forced exploration without stories, without enough rng and deck-building these mode feel very repetitive and not really like the challenges you see in slay the spire. With upgrade materials gated behind end game it’s a catch 22 situation.", "timestamp": "2026-04-10T03:21:03.992000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🔥", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}, {"emoji": "agree", "emoji_id": "1400771815076528258", "count": 2}, {"emoji": "gdoll_evil_laugh", "emoji_id": "1468257456948908094", "count": 1}, {"emoji": "Brown_think", "emoji_id": "1459080117308620996", "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1492001442725105707", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Get Auto enable for dtide", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
{"id": "1492001739044290704", "channel_id": "1492001442725105707", "type": 0, "author_id": "296679098703544321", "author_name": "angbak", "author_bot": false, "content": "Yes, please re enable auto in tide", "timestamp": "2026-04-10T03:22:14.640000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1492001442725105707", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Get Auto enable for dtide", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
{"id": "1491969673452064969", "channel_id": "1491384776911884399", "type": 19, "author_id": "403948418059337728", "author_name": "iulargerthan3", "author_bot": false, "content": "條件能達成  ≠ 合理\n這種在我認知中應該叫 Possible but not reasonable", "timestamp": "2026-04-10T01:14:49.607000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-04-10T01:17:23.420000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": ["776811138984706089"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1491838134605054103", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1491384776911884399", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "建議 14 天課題的學期任務的完成條件應當按天數比例降低", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
{"id": "1491972677798334465", "channel_id": "1491384776911884399", "type": 0, "author_id": "403948418059337728", "author_name": "iulargerthan3", "author_bot": false, "content": "如果要使用當期所有能得到的資源，甚至往期存下來的資源才能完成。這種完成條件就需要被調整了<:dead:1356082627509092372> \n\n畢竟忘卻前夜的課題就等於其他遊戲中的通行證，以 Apex 為例，如果玩家無法通過正常遊玩 ( 不購買等級 ) 去取得應得到的獎勵，就是策劃失誤。\n\nApex 的通行證有一點做的蠻好，就是在付費版的通行證中的獎勵會給出遊戲點數來令玩家有機會每 2 - 3 期能不額外課金來買新一期付費版的通行證。 ( 這與本次建議無關 )\n\n很幸運的是，忘卻前夜的 14 天課題的確不需要完成所有任務來取得應得到的獎勵 ( 暫且忽略溢出等級能取得的金卷 / 藥劑 )，但不代表苛刻的任務完成條件是能被接受的。", "timestamp": "2026-04-10T01:26:45.899000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-04-10T01:48:39.251000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1491384776911884399", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "建議 14 天課題的學期任務的完成條件應當按天數比例降低", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
{"id": "1491981128461062206", "channel_id": "1491384776911884399", "type": 0, "author_id": "403948418059337728", "author_name": "iulargerthan3", "author_bot": false, "content": "不過我感覺我在對空氣爭取，非惡性的玩家福利問題好像不在「有問」就 「必答」的範圍內 <:Brown_think:1459080117308620996>", "timestamp": "2026-04-10T02:00:20.694000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-04-10T02:00:48.447000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1491384776911884399", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "建議 14 天課題的學期任務的完成條件應當按天數比例降低", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
{"id": "1491983671031369758", "channel_id": "1483461060185817318", "type": 19, "author_id": "1485258210209435701", "author_name": "morimensstaff06", "author_bot": false, "content": "Perhaps it's a translation issue, so I'll revise the wording: Some awakened units are positioned to need or be suited to cooperate with others in battle, but Orita is not like that—her strength lies in being effective even without coordination.", "timestamp": "2026-04-10T02:10:26.890000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["298140360603992066"], "reactions": [{"emoji": "dizzy2", "emoji_id": "1356083001926221874", "count": 2}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1491772645866471454", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1483461060185817318", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「Answered」Aurita simple yet effective buff", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361168939622727801"]}
{"id": "1492041898649456650", "channel_id": "1483461060185817318", "type": 19, "author_id": "1437487264023318668", "author_name": "vxvendetta97", "author_bot": false, "content": "Ok, but what we say is that she is not strong by herself or with a dedicated team, and she absolutely need a dedicated team to be at least usable.\nShe and Corposant are the only team that really use the discard mechanic, and have a lot of synergy, but even together they perform worse than others.", "timestamp": "2026-04-10T06:01:49.436000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-04-10T06:04:17.592000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1485258210209435701"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1491983671031369758", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1483461060185817318", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「Answered」Aurita simple yet effective buff", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361168939622727801"]}
{"id": "1492043379289100298", "channel_id": "1483461060185817318", "type": 0, "author_id": "1437487264023318668", "author_name": "vxvendetta97", "author_bot": false, "content": "The change we proposed, even just for the first 2 0 cost cards per turn to not count for the harmony, doesn't seem like a big enough boost to make her unbalanced.", "timestamp": "2026-04-10T06:07:42.448000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1483461060185817318", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「Answered」Aurita simple yet effective buff", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361168939622727801"]}
{"id": "1492044791163256843", "channel_id": "1483461060185817318", "type": 19, "author_id": "1437487264023318668", "author_name": "vxvendetta97", "author_bot": false, "content": "If the team doesn't want to buff her because she is a welfare unit, or because they don't like to receive direct suggestions on discord, we must accept it, but if they want to effectively discuss why they think she or others are in a good balance state, and don't want to make even minor changes, we would appreciate it.\nIf there are translation difficulties, I can enlist the help of a translator.", "timestamp": "2026-04-10T06:13:19.065000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-04-10T06:14:17.425000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1485258210209435701"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1491983671031369758", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1483461060185817318", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「Answered」Aurita simple yet effective buff", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361168939622727801"]}
