{"id": "1492066734968934480", "channel_id": "1483461060185817318", "type": 19, "author_id": "1437487264023318668", "author_name": "vxvendetta97", "author_bot": false, "content": "Ok, this means that the team believes she is strong.\nHowever, in reality, her abilities are limited. She is not useless, but she is not a high-performing character. \nAnd she requires a dedicated team to work properly.\nThe main point is that this small change will not greatly increase her performance. It is only a minor improvement. However, it will improve the gameplay experience and make her more enjoyable to play, without causing real balance problems.", "timestamp": "2026-04-10T07:40:30.876000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-04-10T10:31:34.849000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1485258210209435701"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1492058378690887701", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1483461060185817318", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「Answered」Aurita simple yet effective buff", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361168939622727801"]}
